      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>How To Get A Free Laptop For College</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>5. 12 Organizations Giving Computers To College Students</h4>\n<img alt=\"How To Get A Free Laptop For College_6\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-for-college/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-for-college_6.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-for-college/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-for-college_6.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-for-college/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-for-college_6.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-for-college/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-for-college_6.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>If you find yourself in a tough spot financially, look into these organizations. Many of them require an application and some proof of financial need, but they're great resources to help you get the tech you need for school.</p>\n<p> – <a href=\"https://theonitfoundation.org/\">On It Foundation</a> provides free computers to low-income families</p>\n<p> – <a href=\"https://www.computerswithcauses.org/application/\">Computers With Causes</a> gifts laptops to students.</p>\n<p> – <a href=\"https://www.goodwillfinds.com/electronics/computers-and-tablets/\">Goodwill</a> Industries offers computers and laptops at significantly reduced prices. </p>\n<p> – <a href=\"https://notebooksforstudents.org/\">Notebooks for Students</a> offers students new, refurbished, and discounted laptops.</p>\n</img></div>"
