crosoft Registered Refurbishers</a> offers refurbished, low-cost laptops for educational use.</p>\n<p> – <a href=\"https://www.netliteracy.org/\">Net Literacy</a> distributes repurposed laptops to those in need, including students.</p>\n</img></div>"
